data.title: Dot Dot Dot + Weed Brownies : New Chill Collaboration
data.meta_description: Today I've got a couple new chill tracks, there a collaboration between Wiz Khalifa, Big Sean, and Curren$y. When 3 names like this team up you know its' gonna be sick. Well they are coming out with a mixtape soon, and have been leaking a few of the track off it.
data.text:
Today I've got a couple new chill tracks, there a collaboration between Wiz Khalifa, Big Sean, and Curren$y. When 3 names like this team up you know its' gonna be sick. Well they are coming out with a mixtape soon, and have been leaking a few of the track off it. First I'm featuring Dot Dot Dot, it's got a real mellow chilled out feel, as you'd expect with these 3. The beat is real sick, and all 3 rappers deliver. Also included is Weed Brownies and Flowers. Check them out, chill, and enjoy!

Update: We've never seen the mixtape, these are the only tracks
